Package rw.ac.rca.isomero

Class Book

java.lang.Object
rw.ac.rca.isomero.Book
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable
public class Book extends Object implements Comparable
Represents a book with its unique identifier, name, author, and price. Implements Comparable to allow books to be compared based on price, name, author, and ID. Provides methods to get and set book attributes.
Author:
Livia
